metadata.name: Cake Boss
metadata.summary: Buddy Valastro renowned cake artist & master baker of Carlo’s Bakery.
metadata.description: Buddy Valastro is the Cake Boss. Renowned cake artist & master baker of Carlo’s Bakery, he manages a team including his mother, four sisters & three brothers-in-law. And, when you’re working with family every day, there’s bound to be a lot of drama.
